    "date": "2021-11-16T16:12:34Z",
    "text": "Colonel John McHugh Tuition Fairness for Survivors Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs to disapprove courses of education provided by public institutions of higher learning if such institutions charge a higher rate for tuition and fees than in-state tuition for individuals who are entitled to educational assistance under the Survivors' and Dependents' Educational Assistance program."
